And the beauty of shopping online is we’re open 24/7 so you can shop when it is convenient for you and that means more time playing with your pet.   We have an amazing assortment of pet gear for dogs.  From toys to treats, you’ll find items your pet loves and that you can trust to be good for them.  For long walks in the park, you’ll love our harnesses and leashes and for cooler days our harness coats are just the ticket.   For our furry feline friends, our collection for cats is to be envied.  Your cat will love the selection of pretty cat collars you can choose from – you will certainly find the perfect collar to reflect your feline’s personality.  And when it comes to cat toys and treats, our selection just can’t be beat.   We know your pet is part of the family and there is nothing as cute as dressing them up in adorable outfits for just about any reason.  Our apparel collection for pets is extensive.  From costumes to pajamas, you’ll find fashionable pet clothing your furry friend will adore.  The collection includes formal apparel for special occasions and even motorcycle jackets for those who like to live on the wild side.    When it comes to your home, there is a lot of pet gear you need to make your home comfortable and safe for your pet too.  Pet gates can keep your pet contained and away from trouble.  Scratching posts allow kitties to scratch their claws and save your furniture.  Ramps and stairs prevent injuries to little and old animals and spare your back from lifting them.   Taking care of your pet is a big job and we have the pet accessories you will need to manage it.  From bath tubs and grooming accessories to waste management products, caring for your pet is easy with the right tools.   We know comfort and safety are important to you for your pet.  Our pet beds and travel gear collections keep this in mind.  You’ll find an amazing collection of pet beds that you’ll be tempted to curl up and nap on.  Cats and dogs sleep a lot and they’ll really love catching their z’s on these comfy beds.  Traveling with your pet requires special pet gear.  Whether it is a walk around the block in a stroller, a trip to the vet in a car seat or a vacation where you need a carrier or crate, you’ll find everything you need here.   Finally, at Gear for Pets we love our pets and we know how much you love yours too.  We have a special collection just for the owner.  Aprons come in handy on grooming days.  Tote bags are always convenient and our gifts collection will please any pet lover.     We hope you enjoy shopping our online store for your pet’s needs.  We encourage you to contact us if you have any questions or need any assistance.  We suggest you sign up for our newsletter to receive helpful tips and information and also notice of sales and special discounts.  Check out our blog which will give lots of advice on caring for pets and follow us on social media – Facebook, Twitter and Pinterest to get the latest information and lots of great ideas. Full Description: College Brewer is an e-commerce start-up that makes homebrewing an easy-to-learn and affordable hobby accessible to any college student.  Studies show that 4 out of 5 college students consume beer on a regular basis with the average student drinking 48.3 gallons annually. With over 21 million students currently enrolled in US colleges there is a huge opportunity to introduce homebrewing into an untapped college market.  In 2012, homebrewing generated over $1 billion in annual economic activity, growing at over 20 percent a year. Most of this new growth comes from young adults who are introduced to the DIY brewing craze, yet no one is targeting the enormous beer brazen college market. The perception is that homebrewing is a complicated and expensive hobby. Without any clear direction many would-be brewers are intimidated and give up before they even start. Many that do try homebrewing end up wasting hundreds of dollars on unnecessary equipment, ending up with bad beer. That's a problem…and an opportunity.   That's where College Brewer comes in.  We've simplified homebrewing. Everything has been broken down into the basics so that brewing your own beer is an easy-to-learn and fulfilling hobby. Between our online support, easy to follow instructions, and video database you'll never be stranded without an answer. And not only that, we've made everything affordable. College students are on a budget. Understandable considering they’re entering what is possibly the most debt ridden portion of their life. We’ve developed Brew Kits that allow brewers to make their own beer at college without breaking the bank.  To reach this goal College Brewer is seeking $50,000 in equity investment to fund the business start-up.
Industry Groups: Commerce and Shopping, Education, Internet Services, Other, Social Impact

Description: Voting platform for public issues.
Headquarters Regions: San Francisco Bay Area, Silicon Valley, West Coast
Full Description: GOF is your voting platform for issues ranging from neighborhood concerns to global policy. You communicate your stand on the issues to local, national, and global policy makers. What can you do? 1. Do you have a burning issue or concern? Submit it. 2.Vote “for” or “against” and explain why (if you choose) 3.Invite your friends, neighbors, and fellow citizens—the more the merrier. Besides—greater participation raises your issue to the top of the agenda. Why participate? Voting is the next step beyond petitioning (and having others vote on your behalf). The internet is a great information, access, and organizing tool. Let’s use it to discuss, deliberate, and make our voices count. Together we’ll share and promote views from the ground level. When we own our ideas we’re more inclined to get off our comfy chairs and do something about it in real time. Is it free? You betcha. We want everyone to participate. Our core principles. 1. Non-partisan There is no agenda from the left or right (or anything in between). All opinions are welcome as long as they are respectful of human dignity and diversity. We do reserve the right to flag content that is disrespectful, a violation of human rights, or just plain old spam. We don’t take stands or prioritize issues. We only deliver a live platform that allows all citizens to evoke their point of view and measure its popularity by quantifiable methods. 2. Transparency GOF cannot hide or reserve information about our participants. We will only reserve as private the personal information and activity at the behest of the contributor. The ability to vote is sacred. We have an ongoing commitment to investigate and constantly develop new ways to verify and authenticate the content, votes and contributors on our platform. 3. Human rights are civil rights. We will not accept content that discriminates on the basis of race, class, sex, ethnicity, politicl affiliation, or sexual orientation. Content that represents a violation of Human Rights or contravenes our intent to provide a conduit for open and democratic exchange of ideas will be removed. We are developing new tools that will allow our users to determine if flagged content should be removed by vote. Let us know about your point of view by contacting us at info@gof.do Team We are a dedicated, perspicacious, and small group of engineers,designers and entrepreneurs living in Palo Alto, CA. You can reach us at:contact@gof.do
Industry Groups: Government and Military, Privacy and Security
Founders: Carlos Santos Campos, Luis Enrique Castillo

Some of the doctor reviews are so astounding that a patient in the area needs to be aware of the concerns regarding care given by the doctor. Users find the available information easy to find and the communities active, inspiring and topic reach to cover all areas pertaining to any health care concerns they may have.
